data.description: * UNDER CONTRACT with a 48hr right of refusal* Welcome to 8244 Towncreek Circle, a rare find in the established community of Seven Lakes in Ooltewah, TN. This meticulously maintained townhome offers the convenience of one-level living coupled with the charm of a gated community.Boasting only to be one of four townhomes in this serene neighborhood, residents enjoy exclusive access to community amenities including a community pool and scenic ponds. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior featuring refinished hardwood floors, new light fixtures, and fresh paint throughout. The spacious layout is enhanced by 9-foot ceilings and new baseboards, creating an inviting atmosphere for comfortable living.The heart of the home lies in the modern kitchen, complete with granite countertops and ample cabinetry for storage. Retreat to the master suite featuring a tiled shower, double vanity, and generous closet space.Outside, a 2 car garage and private back deck offers the perfect spot for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. With its desirable Ooltewah location and county taxes, this townhome presents a unique opportunity for convenient yet affordable living.Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Seven Lakes - schedule your showing today and experience the best of Ooltewah living!
